<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Course Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }

    strong {
      color: #28a745;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Your Course Order Confirmation</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <strong><%= name %>,</strong></p>
      <p>Thank you for ordering the course <strong><%= order.name %></strong>.</p>
      <p>Order ID: <strong><%= order._id %></strong></p>
      <p>Price: $<strong><%= order.price %></strong></p>
      <p>Order Date: <strong><%= order.date %></strong></p>
      <p>We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy the course!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; LearnZilla</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
